org.wildfly.security.credential.store.impl

Class MaskedPasswordStore

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.wildfly.security.credential.store.CredentialStoreSpi
      • org.wildfly.security.credential.store.impl.CommandCredentialStore
        • org.wildfly.security.credential.store.impl.MaskedPasswordStore

  • public class MaskedPasswordStore
extends CommandCredentialStore
    Pseudo credential store which is able to get credential from masked password string. It uses attributes passed to CommandCredentialStore.initialize(Map) for getting additional information to decode the password.
    Author:
    Peter Skopek
